{% comment %}
  Our Story Page Section
  Includes: Hero, Mission Statement, Our Story, and Core Values
{% endcomment %}

<section class="our-story-page">
  <div class="our-story-hero">
    <div
      class="our-story-hero-image"
      style="background-image: url('{{ section.settings.hero_image | image_url }}');"
    >
      <div class="our-story-hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="our-story-hero-content">
        <h1 class="our-story-hero-title">ABOUT US</h1>
        <div class="our-story-hero-underline"></div>
        <div class="our-story-hero-buttons">
          {% render 'cta-button',
            popover: 'newsletter-membership-popover',
            text: 'JOIN THE MOVEMENT',
            class: 'cta-button--secondary'
          %}
          {% render 'cta-button',
            url: '/products/airrail-6-performance-shorts-mountain-mist',
            text: 'TRAIN WITH US',
            class: 'cta-button--secondary'
          %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% comment %} Mission Statement Section {% endcomment %}
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="mission-statement-content">
      <h2 class="mission-statement-title">
        OUR
        <br>
        MISSION
      </h2>
      <div class="mission-statement-underline"></div>
      <div class="mission-statement-box">
        Create the most lightweight and breathable training gear,
        <br>
        while building a community that pushes you further.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="our-mission-content">
      <h2 class="our-mission-title">
        FITNESS IS MORE THAN MOVEMENT, <br>
        IT'S MOMENTUM
      </h2>
      <div class="our-mission-box">
        <div class="our-mission-text">
          The most growth happens when you sweat together. We exist to inspire each other through training, mindset, and
          the power of community. Every product, every session, and every rep is designed to fuel progress together.
          <br>
          <br>
          We found a lot of brands out there try to be many things to many people. Clothes that are designed to do
          everything okay, but nothing great. We're not that brand.
          <br>
          <br>
          We're creating gear that was designed for one purpose: Be as light and breathable as possible so you only ever
          have to focus on the workout at hand.
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ section.settings.mission_image | image_url }}"
          alt="{{ section.settings.mission_title }}"
          class="our-mission-image"
          loading="lazy"
          width="400"
          height="600"
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="our-story-mission-underline"></div>

    {% comment %} Our Story Section {% endcomment %}
    <div class="our-story-content">
      <h2 class="our-story-title">OUR STORY</h2>
      <div class="our-story-container">
        <img
          src="{{ section.settings.our_story_image | image_url }}"
          alt="Our Story Image"
          class="our-story-image"
          loading="lazy"
          width="400"
          height="600"
        >

        <div class="our-story-text-container">
          <div class="our-story-text">
            Fitness opens doors. Fitness shows us that there’s more out there, more to see, more to chase, more to
            become.
            <br>
            <br>
            For me, it changed everything. It brought me to California to play football, introduced me to my fiancee on
            a volleyball court, and took me skiing across some of the most awe-inspiring places in the world. Wherever
            life led, fitness brought connection through groups big and small that trained hard, showed up, and pushed
            one other further.
            <br>
            <br>

            Through it all, one truth stuck: the discipline we build in training makes every other part of life that
            much better. That’s why 7Pacific exists. To create the kind of gear that keeps up with your pursuit, and a
            community that reminds us we’re never in it alone.

            <br>
            <br>
            We're developing the kind of gear that keeps up with your pursuit. A gear that is lightweight, breathable,
            and durable. A gear that is designed to move with you every step of the way. Whenever you're ready to push
            towards that next challenge, we're here to help you get there.
          </div>
          <div class="our-story-founder-signature">
            <p class="our-story-founder-signature-name">Gabriel Dalessandro</p>
            <p class="our-story-founder-role">Founder & CEO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {% comment %} Core Values Section {% endcomment %}
    {% comment %}
      <div class="our-story-values">
        <div class="page-width">
          <h2 class="our-story-values-title">{{ section.settings.values_title }}</h2>
          <p class="our-story-values-subtitle">{{ section.settings.values_subtitle }}</p>

          <div class="our-story-values-grid">
            {% for i in (1..4) %}
              {% assign value_number = 'value_' | append: i | append: '_number' %}
              {% assign value_title = 'value_' | append: i | append: '_title' %}
              {% assign value_description = 'value_' | append: i | append: '_description' %}

              <div class="our-story-value-item">
                <div class="our-story-value-number">{{ section.settings[value_number] }}</div>
                <h3 class="our-story-value-title">{{ section.settings[value_title] }}</h3>
                <p class="our-story-value-description">{{ section.settings[value_description] }}</p>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endcomment %}
  </div>
</section>

{% comment %}
  Include the newsletter popover that will be triggered by the button
{% endcomment %}
{% render 'newsletter-popover', id: 'newsletter-membership-popover' %}

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
    // Initialize modal for the newsletter popover
    if (window.theme && window.theme.Modals) {
      new theme.Modals('newsletter-membership-popover', 'newsletter-membership-popover');
    }
  });
</script>

